Abstract = {Urban rail transit safety is the top priority of urban public safety,
   and the construction of social security prevention and control system
   needs to be refined. This paper analyses the data characteristics of the
   incidents in the urban rail transit environment, and uses the exception
   correlation analysis method for data mining. The association rules with
