   Refinery \& Petrochem},
Abstract = {As the need of investigative information is increasing at an exponential
   rate, extraction of relevant patterns out of huge amount of forensic
   data becomes more complex. Forensic pattern mining is a technique that
   deals with mining of the forensic patterns from forensic pattern
   warehouse in support of forensic investigation and analysis of the
   causes of occurrence of an event. But, sometimes those patterns do not
   provide certain analytical results and also may contain some noisy
   information with them. An approach through which optimal patterns or
   reliable patterns are extracted from forensic pattern warehouse which
   strengthen the decisions-making process during investigations has been
   proposed in the paper.},
