Organization = {IEEE; IEEE Comp Soc; IEEE Tech Comm Scalable Comp; Univ Exeter},
Abstract = {Data visualization is an innovative method of displaying and analysising
   data. Currently, as more and more users view, analyze, and visualize big
   data through mobile devices, developers face the challenges that how to
   address the visualization of large datasets on mobile devices. This
   paper aims to develop an innovative prototype of data visualization
   application, using open source resources for the visualization
   presentation, which will allow data from the crime and health of
   Yorkopendata and Obesity, Physical Activity and Diet of NHS be
   presented, evaluated and analyzed at anytime and anywhere. D3.js, one of
   the most popular visualization library, was used to beautify the data,
   and then put D3.js integrated into a cross-platform development
   framework PhonrGap to display the data on the device.},
