   Khalid, Sobia, Natl Univ Sci \& Technol, CEME, Dept Comp Engn, Islamabad, Pakistan.
   Khan, Shoab A., Natl Univ Sci \& Technol, CEME, Dept Comp Engn, Islamabad, Pakistan.},
